label: uncl7085
comment: Code specifying the classification of a type of cargo.

values.label: Documents
values.comment: Printed, typed or written matter including leaflets, pamphlets, certificates etc., which are not subject to import duties and taxes, restrictions and prohibitions.

values.label: Low value non-dutiable consignments
values.comment: Imported consignments/items/goods in respect of which Customs duties and other taxes are waived as they are below a value determined by the Customs administration.

values.label: Low value dutiable consignments
values.comment: Imported consignments/items/goods in respect of which Customs duties and other taxes are payable are below a certain amount as determined by the Customs administration.

values.label: High value consignments
values.comment: Imported consignments/items/goods which are determined as having a value above a certain amount fixed by the Customs administration, which may or may not attract duties and taxes.

values.label: Other non-containerized
values.comment: Non-containerized cargo which cannot be categorized by any of the other nature of cargo code.

values.label: Vehicles
values.comment: Vehicles which are not stowed in containers.

values.label: Roll-on roll-off
values.comment: Cargo transported or to be transported on roll-on roll- off vessels and which is transportable on its own wheels or stowed on special heavy duty trailers.

values.label: Palletized
values.comment: Non-containerized cargo which is palletized.

values.label: Containerized
values.comment: Cargo stowed or to be stowed in a container.

values.label: Breakbulk
values.comment: Non-containerized cargo stowed in vessels' holds.

values.label: Hazardous cargo
values.comment: Cargo with dangerous properties, according to appropriate dangerous goods regulations.

values.label: General cargo
values.comment: Cargo of a general nature, not otherwise specified.

values.label: Liquid cargo
values.comment: Cargo in liquid form.

values.label: Temperature controlled cargo
values.comment: Cargo transported under specified temperature conditions.

values.label: Environmental pollutant cargo
values.comment: Cargo is an environmental pollutant.

values.label: Not-hazardous cargo
values.comment: Cargo which is not hazardous.

values.label: Diplomatic
values.comment: Cargo transported under diplomatic conditions.

values.label: Military
values.comment: Cargo for military purposes.

values.label: Obnoxious
values.comment: Cargo that is objectionable to human senses.

values.label: Out of gauge
values.comment: Cargo that has at least one non-standard dimension.

values.label: Household goods and personal effects
values.comment: Cargo consisting of household goods and personal effects.

values.label: Frozen cargo
values.comment: Cargo of frozen products.

values.label: Ballast only
values.comment: No cargo, means of transport is carrying only ballast.

values.label: Incompatible cargo
values.comment: Incompatible cargo to be transported / stored with other types of cargo.

values.label: Deep-frozen cargo
values.comment: Cargo of deep-frozen products.
